    "body": "@prspace We limit the number of returned categories by default to only show the most relevant ones (most counts), can you try with passing the `limit` option?\n\n``` js\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.hierarchicalMenu({\n    // all other options, then\n    limit: 20\n  });\n);\n```\n",
